                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="276697" author="vilapa" created="Wed, 5 Aug 2020 08:46:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;To specify file Project ID it is necessary to enable quota feature.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;According to the Lustre manual.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The project quota feature is disabled by default, and tune2fs needs to be run to enable every target manually.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To turn on user, group, and project quotas for block only on file system testfs1, on the MGS run:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;mgs# lctl conf_param testfs1.quota.ost=ugp&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
